<br>
There's not much reason to leave the Nektulos Forest area till level 12 (when you get Bind Affinity) anyway.  But you might be getting tired of Nek and have started wandering.  <br>
<br>
At any rate, once 12, it's time to venture out.  Take port book in Nektulos Forest to PoK and then go to the Cabilis Book in PoK and port down to Field of Bone.  Follow the zone north, until you see the tower that is Kurn's Tower.<br>
<br>
It's easy to spot as you run up.  Cast invis once you port into FoB and you shouldn't have any problems.  The skellies will see you so be careful but at this level most are green.<br>
<br>
The scorpians will aggro you as you cross the zone, so be careful if you don't want to invis yourself..<br>
<br>
You'll be glad you came here, the xp is very nice.  <br>
<br>
But healers are a rare thing to find so prepare to be having some downtime if take too many hits.   I bound right out front of Kurn's so if I died, I was able to get back in, get corpse and keep killing.  Enjoy.<br>
<br>
Kastin Spellz<br>
